# Intuition
When one player chooses a stone, he dosen't allow the next player to take points of that stone, hence alice and bob can take stones in order of maximum sum of each stone's value(i.e. at ith index, sum will be alice[i]+bob[i]). So if players take stones in order of maximum sum, they will gain maximum points as they will play optimally.

